# AI-Powered Loan Prediction System

## 📌 Overview
This project is a Machine Learning-based web application that predicts whether a loan will be approved or not based on user inputs such as age, income, credit score, loan amount, and employment status.

## 🚀 Features
- User-friendly web interface
- Real-time loan prediction
- Machine Learning model integration
- Flask-based backend
- Deployed on cloud platform

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python
- Flask
- Scikit-learn
- Pandas
- HTML & CSS

## 📊 Input Parameters
- Age
- Income
- Credit Score
- Loan Amount
- Loan Term
- Employment Status

## 🎯 Output
- Loan Approved / Not Approved

## ⚙️ How It Works
1. User enters details in the web form
2. Data is sent to Flask backend
3. Machine Learning model processes input
4. Prediction is displayed on the UI

## 🌐 Deployment
The project is deployed using Render cloud platform.

## 📌 Future Improvements
- Add user authentication
- Improve UI with React
- Add database integration
- Include more advanced ML models

